Title:  Domain Name from Link - /

AKA:    Domain Name from Link

Timestamp: 20230814212342

Seq:    12.3.42

Level:  4 - Subsection

Class:  non-version

Body:

A modifier of '`/`' (forward slash) can be applied to a variable containing a [[Link]] value, in order to display only the domain name of the website, rather than the entire link. 

